JCrew invites you to take offDear JCrew Customer From September thth JCrew is offering a discount on everything in our stores and online at jcrewcom Check out our new fall selection great styles that you can wear any place any timefrom a business meeting to a casual dinner To find your invitation please visit the following URL that you may forward to family friends and colleagues cgibinfloyeGFfSgoCIBKEmAt Heres the fine print To receive the discount simply print the emailinvite please remember that you must have it in order to receive the discount and present it to the cashier at any of our stores Or if you prefer to receive your discount online at jcrewcom you can simply enter the code CORP in the redeem coupon box on the first checkout page Please note that this discount does not apply to online clearance items or in our catalog In addition to special shopping events such as this JCrew also has Corporate Sales where you can get discounts on largequantity orders of apparel and gift cards personalized with your companys name or logo No matter where you work weve got you covered from workwear to business casual After all what you do from to is your business What you wear is ours To request a catalog or for more information visit us at jcrewcomcrewcorp cgibinfloyeGFfSgoCIBKEnAu We hope that you will take advantage of this great offer If you have any questions feel free to contact me directly at Best regards Stephanie Garbarini Director of Brand Marketing Unsubscribe To be removed from the jcrewcom mailing list please go to cgibinfloyeGFfSgoCIBKEoAvemail
